data.description: Welcome to this lovely single-level 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Templeton's Peterson Ranch tract. Situated on a corner lot with mature landscaping, this residence seamlessly combines practicality and functionality.    Inside, the main bedroom features a convenient walk-in closet, dual sinks, and a relaxing soaking tub in the bathroom. The spacious kitchen boasts granite tile counters, a generous food pantry, and an open layout that flows into the main living area.    This home comes complete with essential appliances, including a washer, dryer, refrigerator, and a secure gun safe. The backyard offers an aluminum patio cover, a stamped concrete patio, and a Tuff Shed for your storage needs.    Don't miss the opportunity to explore this charming property. Schedule your showing appointment today and discover the warmth and comfort this home has to offer.
